<%- include('../partials/header') %>

<main class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-primary mb-3"><%= title %></h1>
            
            <p>Welcome! My name is Lourdes Soto. I had the incredible privilege of working as a professional trekking tour guide, designing and leading international expeditions through the high-altitude landscapes, rugged mountain passes, and ancient historical trails of Cusco, Peru.</p>
            
            <p>To me, hiking is much more than a physical trek, it is a metaphor for how we walk through our lives. Each trail brings different experiences, changing weather, and steep obstacles, teaching us how to navigate and overcome challenges. I believe that the end of the trail is never the true goal; the real purpose is found within the journey itself, the resilience we build, and the connections we share along the way.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
            <img src="/images/about-me.jpg" alt="Lourdes Soto Trekking Guide Portfolio Image" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm">
            <div class="mt-2 text-muted small italic">
                <p>Source: Personal professional archive of Lourdes Soto.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>